          </div>
          <div class="w-full px-5 lg:w-1/2">
             <div class="mb-6">
                <label class="block mb-2 text-lg font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Publication Logo for Dark Mode</label><small class="block mb-2 -mt-2 text-base italic text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Publication logo that should appear in dark mode. Recommended dimension: 500px X 125px</small>
                <div class="w-full">
                   <label class="w-full border-2 border-dashed hover:border-blue-600 flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 py-16 rounded-lg tracking-wide uppercase dark:border-slate-800 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">
                      <svg class="w-10 h-10 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 640 512">
